## Verification Plan

### Automated Checks
```bash
# 1. Confirm migration runs clean
cd logihub/backend && alembic upgrade head

# 2. Confirm the FastAPI app starts without errors
# (docker-compose up or uvicorn main:app)

# 3. Test endpoints via curl
# Create a client user
curl -X POST /users -H "Authorization: Bearer <admin_jwt>" \
  -d '{"name":"Test Client","role":"client","phone":"+996771000001"}'

# Fetch catalog as client bot
curl -X GET "/bot/catalog?tg_id=<client_tg_id>" -H "X-Bot-Secret: <secret>"

# Submit client order
curl -X POST /bot/orders/client -H "X-Bot-Secret: <secret>" \
  -d '{"tg_id":<client_tg_id>,"product_id":"...","quantity":1,"delivery_address":"Test"}'
```

### Manual Verification
- Confirm new `client` option appears in the UserCreate form on the frontend
- Confirm Telegram admin notification fires when a client order is submitted
- Confirm order appears in the admin orders list with `status=new`
